#* {{zh-x|總括 先生{sheng} 來信 的 意思{si}，大概 有 兩 點，一 是 罵 ^史太林 先生{sheng}-們 是 官僚，再 一 是 斥 @^毛.^澤東 先生{sheng}-們 的 「各-派 聯合 一致 抗日」的 主張 為{wéi} 出賣 革命。|I take it that the main drift of your letter is contained in these two points: You consider Stalin '''and his colleagues''' bureaucrats, and the proposal of Mao Tsetung '''and others''' — “Let all parties unite to resist Japan” — as a betrayal of the cause of revolution.|ref='''1936''', {{w2|zh|魯迅}} ({{w|Lu Xun}}) (attributed), {{lang|zh|《答托洛斯基派的信》}} (Reply to a Letter from the Trotskyites). English translation from [https://www.marxists.org/archive/lu-xun/1936/06/09.htm]}}
